Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你是哪里来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,费耶尼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么远?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,走过来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在环游阿尔西亚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊 恋人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是传说中的 击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跑得比马还快 还能飞上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候听说过 可飞上天也太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是传闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然事出唐突
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请给我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要钱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经近一周没吃饭快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 说来是个闻者伤心听者落泪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,某位大人委托我出去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我把那笔钱在烟花柳巷里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是遇上意外弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不是一不小心中了邪 或者败给了欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这种应该算是男人的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我至少要把买东西的钱拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不然又要吃不上饭 饿死…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也忍不住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不对好 质朴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,胸比钱要紧? 还是饭要紧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 结婚? 钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,钱 饭 结婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,钱 饭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你出去买东西就没见你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是那家移动酒馆的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 请你吃一顿以表歉意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈小姐 也给我吃饭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给你买东西的钱呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可我已经一周没吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道「不劳者不得食」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我可以请你吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 心疼这种东西也没好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,饭…饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,阳菜 很少见的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么写的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,汉字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,少见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪里出生的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好偏僻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没听说那里还有城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我一直是和妈妈两个人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天妈妈她 突然被大地吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜 是被阿比斯吞噬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿比斯吞噬?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你仔细看看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的身上都刻有数字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界被数字统治着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被数字统治着?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这个国家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一生下来 就有义务为某件事计数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,计数?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,譬如 我的这个77
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是被客人夸奖「好吃」的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,反之要是说「难吃」次数就会减少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上的某个地方 应该也有数字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来 张开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好固执的腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就像刚才说的 点数也会下跌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是女性公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能挣到点数倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不巧让点数不断下跌 归零的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}色魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}变态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就会被阿比斯吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被阿比斯吞噬?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以大家每天都在努力让点数增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力不让点数下跌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被阿比斯吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有的说会直接死在大地之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也有说会被送去比死更恐怖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,另外关于点数 还有重要的一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,数字低的人无法违抗数字比自己高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,无法违抗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你要记牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,点数的差距 等同于身份的高低
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在这层意义上 这个世界也被数字统治着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 小阳菜呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是在给什么计数?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是走过的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈以前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 每走100公里才能涨1点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,411的话 你已经旅行了4万公里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 从5年前开始 一直在找重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惊人 这可不是一般的辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不 算不上辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是妈妈留下的遗言 让我一定要找到那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,每当这个数字增加的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都觉得在和妈妈一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像在鼓励我 一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,既然看得这么重 你找的人也真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个重要的人 到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是带着白色闪耀星星的 传说中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…只是个传说 就像童话故事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我在途中听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的击坠王就在这座镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才过来见那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在这座镇上住了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特 传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 小阳菜 别找什么击坠王…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是在找我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,白色的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,带着白色闪耀星星的 废弃战争的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是…击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 因为我找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一直…都在找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是我的荣幸 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在军队里担任曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,具体就去前面的值班室里说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想违抗军队吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奈奈小姐 里希特先生 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,听说有人假借击坠王之名欺负女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道还…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王在这座镇上的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到传得这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只怪相信的人太傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗? 再这么下去她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,站住啊 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我照妈妈说的 这5年里一直在找击坠王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗? 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 击坠王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,数字球?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是数字球持有者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,数字…那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗? 你不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可这个是妈妈的遗物…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你这女人真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的点数是320吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的点数有441
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,无法违抗点数比自己高的人 是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们赌星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,赌星?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我动用军人的特权 向你发起星夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,区区庶民还不了解吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也罢 只要你不赌星 我就没义务服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办? 要不要赌星?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我赌 只要能让你住手就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,点数低的人无法违抗高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有一个例外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是星夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是赌上自己点数的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些庶民顶多就是听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,星夺战就是只有我们军人才能行使的究极特权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是无上的愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是只属于天选之人的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表情太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要? 你这等于承认自己输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,星夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧 自己的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,胜者能夺走败者的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,将它占为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是星夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你现在的点数是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,1 只剩1了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 打算把数字球交出来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老老实实把数字球交出来 做我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说 你想再赌一次星?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这次肯定会被阿比斯吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做这么残忍的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明是传说中的击坠王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底知不知道什么是传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,击坠王先生是废弃战争的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,带着白色闪耀的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,将打倒敌人的个数刻在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能发挥超乎人类智慧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而我就是传说中的击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哪会有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这种好事 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不知道废弃战争是什么时候的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 废弃战争发生在300年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都300年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就算击坠王的传说是真的 怎么可能还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的击坠王 已经不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,已经…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让你找300年前就消失了的击坠王的妈妈也傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,信她的女儿也蠢得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,5年? 4万公里?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被你妈妈的痴话骗得白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快 把数字球交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说你想再赌一次星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样? 赌不赌?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,赌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你想赌星吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我代她进行星夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你那点数怎么回事? -999?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是下等到底了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,拿这种数字来挑战我 岂止是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,简直是在侮辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看我送你去阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,里希特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不做任何抵抗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你这渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很蹊跷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-999?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大卫曹长 那家伙不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里不对劲?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是-999啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 是下等到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我意思是 明明点数已经跌破零了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙也没被阿比斯吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说明他抵消了 -999的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,靠他的另一个点数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,违法所持者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}数字球持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你 头发清爽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 小阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别再找什么击坠王了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是什么英雄 只不过是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 别再找什么击坠王了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,过上一般的幸福生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-可是…  -你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 你怀着对妈妈的信任一路走来的5年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,4万公里的路途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,决不能任人侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,从她身上夺走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,点数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 这家伙不是单纯的违法所持者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是…那颗星星是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,带着白色闪耀的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,将打倒敌人的个数刻在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能发挥超乎人类智慧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的 击坠王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:56.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}「传说中的击坠王」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我是里希特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下集「星掠者」是内裤狂欢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤 内裤 内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么喜欢内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小阳菜 给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:41.41,Next,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1250,840)}下集「我恨你!」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 「我恨你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,————————OP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}拖着沉重的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}行走着寻找希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:27.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即使受挫 也迈出第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}无法分担的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}被撕扯的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:39.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}如果需要同伴 我就在你身边
